author: 4 Ever Green
description:
Sometimes nature follows the rules and sometimes it completely ignores them.
From horned rabbits and zombie bees to melting starfish and glowing puppies, these animals look like horror-movie creations but are absolutely real.
In this countdown, we explore 15 of the strangest animal phenomena ever recorded, caused by parasites, pollution, disease, and pure biological chaos.
⚠️ Watch till the end for the deer whose antlers never stop growing.
title: 15 Animals Nature Accidentally Turned Into Nightmares
